---
title: "Figure 5.6: Sequence Diagram — Scholarship Search and Retrieval"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant PH as PortalRequestHandler
    participant DB as Database

    B->>PH: GET /scholarships
    PH->>DB: SELECT * FROM scholarships ORDER BY id DESC
    DB-->>PH: All scholarship records
    PH-->>B: Render scholarships.html (full list)

    B->>PH: GET /scholarships?q=engineering
    PH->>DB: SELECT * FROM scholarships WHERE name LIKE '%engineering%' OR description LIKE '%engineering%' OR provider LIKE '%engineering%'
    DB-->>PH: Matching scholarship records
    PH-->>B: Render scholarships.html (filtered results)

    B->>PH: GET /scholarships?q=helb
    PH->>DB: SELECT * FROM scholarships WHERE name LIKE '%helb%' OR description LIKE '%helb%' OR provider LIKE '%helb%'
    DB-->>PH: Matching scholarship records
    PH-->>B: Render scholarships.html (filtered results)
